    <item>
      <title>CAPS Core</title>
      <link>//localhost:3000/reference/caps-core/core/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:3000/reference/caps-core/core/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This page shows the source-documented &lt;code&gt;FsFlow.Caps.Core&lt;/code&gt; surface: the clock, random, GUID, and environment-variable capabilities, plus the live and deterministic providers used by production and tests.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;capability-types&#34;&gt;Capability types&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type &lt;a href=&#34;./iclock.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;IClock&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Provides synchronous access to the current UTC clock. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L8&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type &lt;a href=&#34;./irandom.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;IRandom&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Provides synchronous random-number generation. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L13&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type &lt;a href=&#34;./iguid.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;IGuid&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Provides synchronous GUID generation. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L18&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type &lt;a href=&#34;./ienvironmentvariables.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;IEnvironmentVariables&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Provides synchronous environment-variable lookup. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L23&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type &lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariableerror.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariableError&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Describes a meaningful environment-variable failure. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L29&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;constructors&#34;&gt;Constructors&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;MissingVariable of name: string&lt;/code&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L31&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;InvalidVariable of name: string * value: string * expected: string&lt;/code&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L34&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;clock&#34;&gt;Clock&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;Clock&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for clock capabilities. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L38&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./clock-now.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Clock.now&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads the current UTC timestamp from a clock capability. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L40&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./clock-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Clock.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a live clock backed by &lt;code&gt;UtcNow&lt;/code&gt;. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L43&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./clock-fromvalue.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Clock.fromValue&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a deterministic clock that always returns the supplied instant. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L48&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;random&#34;&gt;Random&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;Random&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for random-number capabilities. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L54&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./random-nextint.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Random.nextInt&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a random integer from a random capability. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L56&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./random-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Random.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a live random-number generator backed by &lt;code&gt;Random&lt;/code&gt;. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L60&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./random-fromvalue.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Random.fromValue&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a deterministic random generator that always returns the supplied value. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L69&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;guid&#34;&gt;GUID&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;Guid&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for GUID capabilities. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L75&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./guid-newguid.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Guid.newGuid&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a GUID from a GUID capability. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L77&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./guid-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Guid.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a live GUID generator backed by &lt;code&gt;NewGuid&lt;/code&gt;. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L80&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./guid-fromvalue.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;Guid.fromValue&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a deterministic GUID generator that always returns the supplied value. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L85&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;environment-variables&#34;&gt;Environment variables&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariables&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for environment-variable providers. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L91&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariables-tryget.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariables.tryGet&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a raw environment-variable value from a provider. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L93&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariables-live.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariables.live&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a live provider backed by the current process environment. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L97&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariables-frompairs.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariables.fromPairs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Creates a deterministic provider from a fixed set of name/value pairs. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L105&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariable&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for reading and parsing environment variables. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L119&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariable-tryget.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariable.tryGet&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a raw string environment variable without wrapping it in a result. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L140&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariable-get.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariable.get&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a raw string environment variable. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L134&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariable-getint.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariable.getInt&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads an integer environment variable. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L144&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariable-getguid.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariable.getGuid&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a GUID environment variable. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L151&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariable-getbool.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariable.getBool&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Reads a boolean environment variable. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L158&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;module &lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariableErrors&lt;/code&gt;: Helpers for formatting environment-variable errors. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L166&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;./environmentvariableerrors-describe.md&#34; class=&#34;broken-link&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;EnvironmentVariableErrors.describe&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Formats a human-readable description for an error. &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adz/FsFlow/blob/main/src/FsFlow.Caps.Core/Core.fs#L168&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
